title: Episode #45: Interview with Rusty Labuschagne Part 1
description:
One of the most interesting and powerful interviews I have done!
In this episode I interview Rusty Labuschagne who was unjustly thrown into prison for ten years even though he was innocent! In this interview, he recounts his horrendous story of life in prison, and how he used his mind to overcome the trauma and forgive those who hurt him. This is truly a testimony to the power of our minds! 
For more info on Rusty and to get his book click here: https://beatingchains.com 
Part 2 will be out next week!
